<template>
  <el-table
      :data="tableData"
      style="width: 100%"
  >
    <el-table-column align="center" label="ID" width="100" type="index">
    </el-table-column>

    <el-table-column
        prop="enId"
        label="需求Id"
        width="180"
    >
    </el-table-column>

    <el-table-column
        prop="graduateId"
        label="毕业生id"
        width="180"
    >
    </el-table-column>

    <el-table-column
        prop="rpPhase"
        label="招聘进度"
    >
    </el-table-column>

    <el-table-column
        label="操作"
        width="100">
      <template slot-scope="scope">
        <el-button @click="goto(scope.row)" type="text" size="small">查看</el-button>
      </template>
    </el-table-column>
  </el-table>
</template>

<script>
export default {

  data() {
    return {
      tableData: [
      {
        enId: '1',
        graduateId: '6',
        rpPhase: '简历审核'
      }]
    }
  },

  methods: {
    goto(row) {
      this.$router.push("/")
    }
  }
}
</script>
